      <body>@DHH, I really think we should *not* call `#compact` on the array. Keeping `File.join`'s API sounds better. (And I think there are potential security issues if we silently remove nils from args).</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;@DHH, I really think we should &lt;em&gt;not&lt;/em&gt; call
&lt;code&gt;#compact&lt;/code&gt; on the array. Keeping
&lt;code&gt;File.join&lt;/code&gt;'s API sounds better. (And I think there are
potential security issues if we silently remove nils from
args).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
